WEBVTT

00:08:28.661 --> 00:08:30.841
I started my first group

00:08:32.016 --> 00:08:33.300
of grandmothers.

00:08:33.324 --> 00:08:36.846
(Applause)

00:08:37.186 --> 00:08:38.336
Thank you.

00:08:38.360 --> 00:08:40.639
(Applause)

00:08:41.229 --> 00:08:44.564
Today, there are hundreds of grandmothers

00:08:44.588 --> 00:08:47.384
who are working
in more than 70 communities.

00:08:48.844 --> 00:08:50.672
And in the last year alone,

00:08:51.371 --> 00:08:56.296
more than 30,000 people received treatment

00:08:56.320 --> 00:08:57.837
on the Friendship Bench

00:08:57.861 --> 00:09:01.228
from a grandmother
in a community in Zimbabwe.